videos.headline: Iowa takes lead with passing TD
videos.description: Nathan Stanley connects with Nick Easley for a 5-yard touchdown pass, giving Iowa a 7-3 lead over Illinois.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Iowa takes lead with passing TD) 2017/10/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Illinois ties game with rushing TD
videos.description: Running back Ra'Von Bonner rushes up the middle for a 2-yard touchdown, as the Illini tie the Hawkeyes at 10.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Illinois ties game with rushing TD) 2017/10/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Iowa scores TD before halftime
videos.description: Nathan Stanley passes to running back Akrum Wadley for a 2-yard touchdown as the Hawkeyes go into halftime with a 17-13 lead over the Illini.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Iowa scores TD before halftime) 2017/10/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Iowa extends lead with 39-yard TD
videos.description: Nathan Stanley finds Matt VandeBerg across the middle for a 39-yard Iowa touchdown, as they extend their lead on Illinois 31-16.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Iowa extends lead with 39-yard TD) 2017/10/07 ESHEET
